script MultiQueryDemo

// This sample exercises all three query types the grammar supports.
// In Phase I, only 'find bytes' generates full codegen.
// 'find calls' and 'find functions' parse correctly but their handlers
// are stubs for Phase I (emit empty strings). See README.txt.

// Fully-implemented query: find bytes
find bytes "C3" from 0x00401000

// Stub queries: parse cleanly, no codegen emitted
find calls to "malloc"
find functions where xrefs > 5
